Text:
A little worried when the first song apparently cut off after 36 seconds and the second also ends abruptly. I noticed some distortion near the end of the 3rd song, and haven't tried the rest.

Download was SCREAMING fast (thank you, seeders) and I got the entire album in about 4 minutes. I wonder if there's a relationship there...

It's also miscategorized as an audio book.  Just sayin'.

Be that as it may, thanks for the upload!
